<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="944000000t" end="1018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">关于现在引起混乱的巨大怪兽 我认为与党已经尽了最大努力</p>
<p begin="1018000000t" end="1029000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">这就叫最大努力?</p>
<p begin="1029000000t" end="1042000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">别装蒜了</p>
<p begin="1042000000t" end="1064000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">根本就是束手无策嘛</p>
<p begin="1086000000t" end="1159000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">但实际上政府在御友岛事件发生的时候 是否已就经得知巨大怪兽的存在</p>
<p begin="1160000000t" end="1181000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">这一点我想请总理回答</p>
<p begin="1189000000t" end="1205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">内阁总理大臣</p>
<p begin="1217000000t" end="1238000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">没有这样的事实</p>
<p begin="1250000000t" end="1263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">古茂田孝一</p>
<p begin="1271000000t" end="1307000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">那就是说政府完全不清楚怪兽的存在</p>
<p begin="1296000000t" end="1307000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">不是都已经说了吗</p>
<p begin="1309000000t" end="1328000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">你是不是没得可问了</p>
<p begin="1314000000t" end="1392000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">那之后两次怪兽出现的时候 政府几乎没有对策 也没有出动国防军</p>
<p begin="1393000000t" end="1441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">对于这件事 首相是否承认政府在应对上有疏漏</p>
<p begin="1445000000t" end="1461000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">内阁总理大臣</p>
<p begin="1473000000t" end="1538000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">这件事超乎人们的常识 不得不承认政府的反应有些迟</p>
<p begin="1544000000t" end="1585000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">但我不认为政府的决定有错误</p>
<p begin="1588000000t" end="1607000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">政府的反应太慢了</p>
<p begin="1610000000t" end="1623000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">古茂田孝一</p>
<p begin="1637000000t" end="1681000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">我这里有一份名叫Zearth报告的文书</p>
<p begin="1694000000t" end="1725000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">首相想必知道这份报告书的存在吧</p>
<p begin="1748000000t" end="1763000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">内阁总理大臣</p>
<p begin="1791000000t" end="1801000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">我不知道</p>
<p begin="1806000000t" end="1834000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">根据这份文书 御友岛地震的时候</p>
<p begin="1834000000t" end="1896000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">卫星捕捉到了巨大怪兽 现通称Zearth的影像</p>
<p begin="1900000000t" end="1999000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">并且在政府的委托下 民营企业长谷川Build的认知工程学研究所对Zearth进行了研究</p>
<p begin="2000000000t" end="2044000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">对于这些内容 首相真的完全不清楚么</p>
<p begin="2060000000t" end="2076000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">内阁总理大臣</p>
<p begin="2092000000t" end="2138000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">对于这份文书 我完全没有印象</p>
<p begin="2171000000t" end="2185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">古茂田孝一</p>
<p begin="2190000000t" end="2246000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">真的是这样么 这份文书记载了许多惊人的内容</p>
<p begin="2247000000t" end="2317000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">比如 上边写道当时有数名中学生被困在巨大机器人内部</p>
<p begin="2340000000t" end="2356000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">这是不是事实</p>
<p begin="2374000000t" end="2390000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">内阁总理大臣</p>
<p begin="2415000000t" end="2432000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">我不认为这是事实</p>
<p begin="2459000000t" end="2473000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">古茂田孝一</p>
<p begin="2484000000t" end="2565000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">今后 政府对于巨大怪兽 具体会采取什么措施</p>
<p begin="2578000000t" end="2649000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我们将牢记在灾难中牺牲的国民的痛苦 尽全力研究对策</p>
<p begin="2670000000t" end="2690000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">古茂田议员 请谈谈您的看法</p>
<p begin="2692000000t" end="2715000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">您是怎么得到Zearth报告的</p>
<p begin="2717000000t" end="2776000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">那上边真的有孩子么</p>
<p begin="2776000000t" end="2840000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">古茂田议员对于Zearth报告的来源一言不发 离开了国会</p>
<p begin="2844000000t" end="2883000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">不过机器人上边有中学生这件事实在让人吃惊</p>
<p begin="2885000000t" end="2919000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">确实 如果这是事实 政府必须尽快想办法</p>
<p begin="2931000000t" end="2954000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">广告之后是体育新闻</p>
<p begin="2983000000t" end="2999000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">事件就要开始发展了</p>
<p begin="3010000000t" end="3027000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">接下来会怎么样呢</p>
<p begin="3031000000t" end="3081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">放心吧 爱子 相信爸爸</p>
<p begin="3087000000t" end="3115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">第 16 话 真面目</p>
<p begin="3124000000t" end="3160000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">真想不到那怪物上边有小孩</p>
<p begin="3162000000t" end="3214000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">古茂田议员的原话是"被困在"了上边 不知道有没有什么含义</p>
<p begin="3230000000t" end="3260000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">电视节目真没意思</p>
<p begin="3265000000t" end="3292000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我去买点喝的吧</p>
<p begin="3297000000t" end="3323000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">不用了 喝多了还得上厕所</p>
<p begin="3345000000t" end="3350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">郁子</p>
<p begin="3357000000t" end="3370000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">是你</p>
<p begin="3373000000t" end="3399000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">你怎么搞得 没事吧</p>
<p begin="3418000000t" end="3426000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">还好</p>
<p begin="3453000000t" end="3487000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">对不起 我应该在你身边</p>
<p begin="3519000000t" end="3556000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">洋介 去给我买点什么喝的吧</p>
<p begin="3620000000t" end="3677000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">不是你的错 我太累了</p>
<p begin="3682000000t" end="3712000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">正好借这个机会 好好休息吧</p>
<p begin="3713000000t" end="3748000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">那怎么行 我得赶快找工作</p>
<p begin="3751000000t" end="3789000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">现在的工作顺利的话 不久能有一笔收入</p>
<p begin="3797000000t" end="3815000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">暂时不用发愁了</p>
<p begin="3818000000t" end="3882000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">又那么拼命 你应该为自己活着</p>
<p begin="3886000000t" end="3953000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我不会怪你 也不想拴着你 如果和我过不下去的话…</p>
<p begin="3953000000t" end="3989000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">你在说什么 我从来也没这么想过</p>
<p begin="3994000000t" end="4017000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">只是最近太忙 不小心走偏了路而已</p>
<p begin="4024000000t" end="4050000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">我不会忘了你和洋介的</p>
<p begin="4132000000t" end="4137000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">洋介</p>
<p begin="4151000000t" end="4188000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">爸爸要去工作了 好好照顾妈妈</p>
<p begin="4198000000t" end="4224000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">明天应该能回家了</p>
<p begin="4237000000t" end="4262000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">爸爸 你是真心的么</p>
<p begin="4280000000t" end="4325000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">如果只是为了应付 那没必要</p>
<p begin="4336000000t" end="4359000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">不要再对妈妈假装温柔了</p>
<p begin="4381000000t" end="4421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">你这孩子怎么说起大人话了</p>
<p begin="4429000000t" end="4462000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">别担心 和妈妈在家里等我</p>
<p begin="4468000000t" end="4524000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">现在的工作这两天就能结束 咱么就可以一起好好过日子了</p>
<p begin="4551000000t" end="4559000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">买回来了</p>
<p begin="4587000000t" end="4648000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">男人真是没办法 永远都长不大</p>
<p begin="4689000000t" end="4723000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我不太理解大人</p>
<p begin="4736000000t" end="4776000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">我想 你爸爸肯定很帅吧</p>
<p begin="4778000000t" end="4793000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">有关系么</p>
<p begin="4798000000t" end="4815000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">帅才会招女人喜欢啊</p>
<p begin="4825000000t" end="4832000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">帅么</p>
<p begin="4837000000t" end="4855000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">我觉得算不上</p>
<p begin="4862000000t" end="4899000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">你爸爸和那女人结果怎么样</p>
<p begin="4903000000t" end="4959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">不知道 但最近每天都回家 大概分手了吧</p>
<p begin="4960000000t" end="4992000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">那不是挺好么 你妈妈也有精神了吧</p>
<p begin="5003000000t" end="5018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">那倒也没有</p>
<p begin="5028000000t" end="5037000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">为什么</p>
<p begin="5043000000t" end="5090000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">工作还是找不到 我爸爸的工作收入又不稳定</p>
<p begin="5094000000t" end="5150000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">一个人呆在家里 总是胡思乱想</p>
<p begin="5152000000t" end="5179000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">为这种事发愁啊</p>
<p begin="5190990000t" end="5215000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">不就是工作么 这还不简单</p>
<p begin="5220000000t" end="5280000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">我监狱时的朋友在锦系町开定食店 应该能帮上忙</p>
<p begin="5290000000t" end="5303000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">交给我吧</p>
<p begin="5383000000t" end="5403000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">古茂田议员 您真是厉害</p>
<p begin="5406000000t" end="5431000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">首相惊慌失措的样子实在滑稽</p>
<p begin="5433000000t" end="5487000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">嗯 这次让与党丢了脸 我们的党首也相当高兴</p>
<p begin="5494000000t" end="5553000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">但这种问题就让他慌成那样 难道还有什么内幕</p>
<p begin="5556000000t" end="5623000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">我想应该是的 其实我并不希望认知研的名字浮出水面</p>
<p begin="5625000000t" end="5649000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">但国民有权利知道这些</p>
<p begin="5651000000t" end="5699000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">我只是担心研究会因此出现障碍</p>
<p begin="5710000000t" end="5748000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">吉川教授 切江体内的芯片 有什么成果么</p>
<p begin="5752000000t" end="5801000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">很有成果 我们得到了非常有用的数据</p>
<p begin="5812000000t" end="5833000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">我的女儿也能安全么</p>
<p begin="5837000000t" end="5881000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">不 解除契约的方法还没找到</p>
<p begin="5892000000t" end="5909000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">原来如此</p>
<p begin="5917000000t" end="5978000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">切江的数据显示出个体差异的存在</p>
<p begin="5982000000t" end="6030000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">我准备让我儿子协助研究 希望各位也能帮忙</p>
<p begin="6032000000t" end="6110000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">吉川教授 我们不想女孩子的身体有什么损伤</p>
<p begin="6110000000t" end="6137000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">各位的心情我理解 但是…</p>
<p begin="6138000000t" end="6206000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">我和她商量 但是这问题不那么简单 请给我时间</p>
<p begin="6212000000t" end="6219000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">好</p>
<p begin="6231000000t" end="6252000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">接下来说说节目的事</p>
<p begin="6257000000t" end="6316000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">我们准备制作Zearth的特别节目 希望采访孝美和宽治</p>
<p begin="6318000000t" end="6357000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">当然我们绝对保护她们的安全 也不会公开相貌</p>
<p begin="6357000000t" end="6378000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">节目的内容呢</p>
<p begin="6379000000t" end="6432000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">孩子们结下契约的经过 Zearth或许是地外物质的事实</p>
<p begin="6434000000t" end="6496000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">他们为地球而战的心情 对战死的同伴的怀念 等等</p>
<p begin="6496000000t" end="6507000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">等等</p>
<p begin="6515000000t" end="6560000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">关于驾驶员生死的问题 我希望先不要公开</p>
<p begin="6567000000t" end="6641000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">孩子们因为契约被束缚 无法摆脱战斗 目前先这样为好</p>
<p begin="6642000000t" end="6683000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">可是这样无法带动舆论的</p>
<p begin="6688000000t" end="6739000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">话是没错 但轻举妄动会搅乱国民的感情</p>
<p begin="6750000000t" end="6759000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">确实</p>
<p begin="6769000000t" end="6791000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">往住先生 现在还是慎重为好</p>
<p begin="6866000000t" end="6893000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">你妈妈最近怎么样</p>
<p begin="6899000000t" end="6962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">不敢相信 似乎变年轻了一样 每天还化起妆来</p>
<p begin="6965000000t" end="7008000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">那就是没事了吧 为什么还非要去看</p>
<p begin="7010000000t" end="7040000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">不是因为担心 是去吃饭</p>
<p begin="7048000000t" end="7064000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">到了 就是这</p>
<p begin="7079000000t" end="7091000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">真热闹</p>
<p begin="7091000000t" end="7102000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">欢迎</p>
<p begin="7104000000t" end="7124000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">啊 是阿保 洋介也来了</p>
<p begin="7128000000t" end="7148000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">店长 阿保来了</p>
<p begin="7152000000t" end="7174000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">您来了</p>
<p begin="7177000000t" end="7193000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">正好路过</p>
<p begin="7194000000t" end="7224000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">来吃点什么吧 正好进了点鲜鱼</p>
<p begin="7225000000t" end="7261000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">是么 我本来想喝口水就走的</p>
<p begin="7261000000t" end="7300000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">您这叫什么话 当时那么受您照顾</p>
<p begin="7302000000t" end="7332000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">现在又给我介绍了这么一位好帮手</p>
<p begin="7333000000t" end="7372000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">让您就这么回去了 我的脸往哪放</p>
<p begin="7375000000t" end="7417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">那好 就尝尝你的鲜鱼吧</p>
<p begin="7419000000t" end="7432000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">这才对嘛</p>
<p begin="7438000000t" end="7463000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">大家过来坐 来</p>
<p begin="7475000000t" end="7525000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">切江说的还真没错 你真是变漂亮了</p>
<p begin="7526000000t" end="7546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">瞧您说的</p>
<p begin="7548000000t" end="7581000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">这么一来 他爸爸是不是该担心了</p>
<p begin="7583000000t" end="7612000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">所以现在每天都按时回家</p>
<p begin="7613000000t" end="7646000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">洋介 当着外人瞎说什么呢</p>
<p begin="7647000000t" end="7659000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">不过 小少爷</p>
<p begin="7663000000t" end="7683000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">小…少爷?</p>
<p begin="7686000000t" end="7736000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">你妈妈真是个好人 我脾气不好 谁都干不长</p>
<p begin="7743000000t" end="7807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">可你妈妈从来不生气 帮了我大忙 了不得的忍耐力啊</p>
<p begin="7810000000t" end="7857000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">而且多亏了她 这店的客人越来越多</p>
<p begin="7861000000t" end="7946000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">你可别动什么心眼 她丈夫可非常帅的</p>
<p begin="7946000000t" end="7962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">您放心</p>
<p begin="7964000000t" end="7993000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">您又瞎说</p>
<p begin="7993000000t" end="8024000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">别骗人 心里同意着呢吧</p>
<p begin="8024000000t" end="8038000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">您可真会说</p>
<p begin="8052000000t" end="8081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">想不到人真的能变化这么大</p>
<p begin="8117000000t" end="8156000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">吃饱了 真不错</p>
<p begin="8184000000t" end="8192000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">怎么了</p>
<p begin="8204000000t" end="8231000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">我决定战斗</p>
<p begin="8242000000t" end="8300000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">我其实不知道这世界是否值得我们去保护</p>
<p begin="8308000000t" end="8341000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">但是妈妈那么努力重新站了起来</p>
<p begin="8348000000t" end="8381000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">为了妈妈 我必须战斗</p>
<p begin="8410000000t" end="8456000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">保叔叔 今后也请您代我照顾妈妈</p>
<p begin="8461000000t" end="8489000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">战斗以后 我也就回不来了</p>
<p begin="8496000000t" end="8538000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">别这么说 或许不会死呢</p>
<p begin="8541000000t" end="8564000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">哪有那么合适的</p>
<p begin="8565000000t" end="8593000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">上次不就没有么</p>
<p begin="8598000000t" end="8657000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">我身体能力差 或许战斗力很低</p>
<p begin="8667000000t" end="8721000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">在我们黑道上 你这样的是最可怕的</p>
<p begin="8724000000t" end="8775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">你了解自己 在清楚自己的实力的基础上不畏惧敌人</p>
<p begin="8780000000t" end="8834000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">像你这样的人 是最厉害的</p>
<p begin="8842000000t" end="8856000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">你一定能成功</p>
<p begin="8984000000t" end="9028000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">不知道过程如何 不过结果还是准备战斗了?</p>
<p begin="9042000000t" end="9065000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">又是没见过的地方</p>
<p begin="9071000000t" end="9084000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">似乎又是"客场"</p>
<p begin="9086000000t" end="9119000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">敌人会不会又自杀呢</p>
<p begin="9154000000t" end="9170000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">看来是不会了</p>
<p begin="9177000000t" end="9226000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">切江 我也不知道该说什么好 加油吧</p>
<p begin="9229000000t" end="9255000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">我尽力</p>
<p begin="9262000000t" end="9273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">来了</p>
<p begin="9433000000t" end="9443000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">躲开了?</p>
<p begin="9450000000t" end="9457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">大概是</p>
<p begin="9573000000t" end="9593000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">脚法不错嘛</p>
<p begin="9594000000t" end="9615000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">头一次看到这样的动作</p>
<p begin="9642000000t" end="9668000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">或许是到现在为止最强的对手</p>
<p begin="9774000000t" end="9779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">跳起来了</p>
<p begin="9917000000t" end="9930000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">战法也很干脆</p>
<p begin="9937000000t" end="9951000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">一点多余的动作也没有</p>
<p begin="9989000000t" end="10013000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">幸亏敌人这么弱</p>
<p begin="10014000000t" end="10043000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">没有这回事 你看看敌人的眼睛</p>
<p begin="10073000000t" end="10099000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">已经战斗了很多次了</p>
<p begin="10240000000t" end="10265000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">这么简单 太没意思了</p>
<p begin="10267000000t" end="10280000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">别那么多事了</p>
<p begin="10288000000t" end="10330000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">那么我该跟大家说再见了</p>
<p begin="10335000000t" end="10373990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">接下来的战斗恐怕会更难 加油吧</p>
<p begin="10380000000t" end="10392000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">切江…</p>
<p begin="10397000000t" end="10443000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">最后 我有件事想说</p>
<p begin="10452000000t" end="10458990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">什么</p>
<p begin="10497000000t" end="10560000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">我知道了 没有结契约的是町吧</p>
<p begin="10648000000t" end="10697000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">你说什么呢 不是的</p>
<p begin="10707000000t" end="10729000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">切江 你为什么这么认为</p>
<p begin="10735000000t" end="10795000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">是上次战斗 敌人倒下以后的事 我觉得很奇怪</p>
<p begin="10806000000t" end="10844000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">Zearth现在把切江认定为驾驶员</p>
<p begin="10848000000t" end="10895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">只要这个认定没有取消 下一场战斗他还得战斗</p>
<p begin="10906000000t" end="10914000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">确实</p>
<p begin="10917000000t" end="10940000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">不 那只是…</p>
<p begin="10941000000t" end="10986000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">那时候我想起来了 自然学校时候的事</p>
<p begin="10991000000t" end="11041000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">是你把我们带进那洞的吧</p>
<p begin="11129000000t" end="11148000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">那…</p>
<p begin="11151000000t" end="11177000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">没错吧 肥虫</p>
<p begin="11188000000t" end="11220000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">既然被看穿了 没办法</p>
<p begin="11232000000t" end="11268000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">认了吧 谁让你那么笨</p>
<p begin="11277000000t" end="11344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">她和可可贝利不是你们的地球的人 是从别的地球被送来的</p>
<p begin="11356000000t" end="11369000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">为了什么</p>
<p begin="11373000000t" end="11432000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">召集15名驾驶员结下契约 这就是他们的任务</p>
<p begin="11449000000t" end="11457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">我…</p>
<p begin="11463000000t" end="11475000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">别开玩笑了…</p>
<p begin="11486000000t" end="11498000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">别开玩笑了!</p>
<p begin="11513000000t" end="11555000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">你知道大家战斗的时候是什么心情吗 你知道大家有多痛苦吗</p>
<p begin="11556000000t" end="11560000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">爱子</p>
<p begin="11567000000t" end="11597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">全都是因为你 全都是你的错</p>
<p begin="11597000000t" end="11604000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">住手吧</p>
<p begin="11643000000t" end="11657000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">切江已经死了</p>
<p begin="11823000000t" end="11852000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">太过分了 这太过分了</p>
<p begin="11858000000t" end="11896000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">为什么 为什么大家…</p>
<p begin="11896000000t" end="11962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">往住 别闹了 你把她打坏了怎么办</p>
<p begin="11967000000t" end="12002000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">她毕竟是我妹妹</p>
<p begin="12168000000t" end="12185000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">以上是天气预报</p>
<p begin="12190000000t" end="12212000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">天气渐渐凉起来了</p>
<p begin="12214000000t" end="12237000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">是啊 各位观众也注意不要感冒</p>
<p begin="12248000000t" end="12274000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">刚刚收到的消息…</p>
<p begin="12297000000t" end="12308000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">往住?</p>
<p begin="12328000000t" end="12395000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">刚刚收到的消息 关于古茂田议员在国会提交的Zearth报告</p>
<p begin="12410000000t" end="12449000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">那是我出于兴趣写出 寄给古茂田议员的</p>
<p begin="12455000000t" end="12479000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">我现在无业 希望能成为小说家</p>
<p begin="12482000000t" end="12538000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">但是自己的作品被出版社拒绝 为了消愁写了那报告</p>
<p begin="12543000000t" end="12589000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">看了电视以后 我意识到这件事的严重性 决心出来宣布真相</p>
<p begin="12600000000t" end="12620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">实在对不起</p>
<p begin="12653000000t" end="12664000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">中计了</p>
<p begin="12703000000t" end="12720000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">深夜11点 没有异常</p>
<p begin="12770000000t" end="12788000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">怎么回事 拉警报</p>
<p begin="12790000000t" end="12795000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">是</p>
<p begin="13829000000t" end="13895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">我心里大概一直相信 爸爸会为我解决这一切</p>
<p begin="13904000000t" end="13932000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">下回 情爱</p>
<p begin="13938000000t" end="13958000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">我也要一个人战斗</p>
